Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\bord0\shad0\fs127.5}爱的形状
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,金 我们一起去庆典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说我们俩一起去 好么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我说金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这等烟花盛景 你不好好观看多可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这里真是一处特等席啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要给店里帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 团长还在等我 先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,咱待会儿也过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,咱这个笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是人类与非人类还同处于一个世界的古老故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,亨德里克森 德雷弗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,夺回被两大圣骑士长所支配的王都之战已经结束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是圣战的预兆犹在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如今又将燃起新的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他们说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,七原罪就在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,师父你也喝呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,班 剩饭要变成啤酒味啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你要变成芳香醇厚的猪肉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白回去后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看板娘就是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然后咱和戴安一起去采购
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜店里的大叔说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱的新婚夫妇可享优惠价
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,然后咱问戴安是否觉得困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,结果她说 不 我很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,难不成戴安对咱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真蠢 真蠢 真蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安喜欢的是团长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但之前她又邀请了咱参加庆典
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你去问一下本人不就好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,猪君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候不挑明会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你太没出息了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你也说说他啊 你个混蛋狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,住口 你个混蛋狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让你明白谁更厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,会吃坏肚子的哦 奥斯罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不来一杯么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喝我的酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是一点都不懂得节制啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 豪泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你要出门么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我得吃药了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是让我身体变小的药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是变大的话会吓到大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 小剩饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我会吃得有滋有味的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,小剩饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 金大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有需要的话 我给你倒杯水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白大人 你难道是在收拾么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 团长居然让公主大人做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也只会做这些而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕只能帮上梅利奥达斯大人的一点点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,团长 你听到刚才的话了么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,咱劝你偶尔也要向伊丽莎白大人表达一下感激之情…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我无时无刻不在感激伊丽莎白哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,团长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来 倒是你向人家道谢了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你喝得酩酊大醉 戴安片刻不离陪在你左右
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,整整一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,咱好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,头好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧 金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那是真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安一早就出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她说中午回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,咱…咱去找一下戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,别去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她可能想一个人待着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在之前的战斗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,镇上的人们似乎曾对她施以兵戎 恶语相加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说他们是被德雷弗斯圣骑士长煽动的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但对她来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,或许待在人类的国度本身就是种煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话我都不知道该怎么安慰她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,豪泽尔 你完全没必要安慰她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的交给咱就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经受够人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,别来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,永别了 金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,难道她就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我把那个搬到这里来么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,咱滑啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 多亏了小姑娘你每天过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,修复工作进行得很顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你的力气好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我给这一带的人添过麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,七原罪 嫉妒之罪戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你是那个时候的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我靠玛琳的药变小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一定很怕我 很讨厌我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我吓到了大家 毁坏了小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想为这一切道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你们不原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想尽可能帮上大家的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你要向我们道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才是做了即使道歉也难求原谅的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候我们的行为很过分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一心以为七原罪是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真心感到惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,再不赶紧工作的话 太阳就要下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好勒 各位 重新开工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前先吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你若不介意 就一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可以么 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安 辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你都看到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那你怎么不来一起帮忙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不 咱感觉咱不适合出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话 咱没有原谅那些人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安还是一如既往很善良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一如既往？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你想 咱说的一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那个不是说两百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而是15年前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,两百年前？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,咱有这么说么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,咱和戴安的初遇是在15年前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那两百年前是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…那是…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,咱给你买了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不用啦 我看看就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,金做的衣服更可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是那样么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我说金 你饿不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微有点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你突然怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不 咱就是突然想跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我说金
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,回店里之前 我们来玩追人游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,追人游戏么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我老早想在这镇上玩一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在的大小能玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 这次换我来逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,金要是能抓住我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以答应你任何一个要求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真…真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是能抓住咱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,咱可以答应你任何一个要求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你好狡猾啊 戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,才不狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看咱的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我好怕怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你能飞那么快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还远远不止这点程度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你就这么想让我答应你一件事么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何 咱都要抓到你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,咱想让戴安做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,陪咱约会一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,别黏那么紧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,陪咱睡一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,或者和咱一起戏水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好色呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 然后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 咱跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去咱的野心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那么在此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,二位能够发誓永远爱对方么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我以女神之名 认可二位结为夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好好加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你头上沾了片花瓣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,金 你知道么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,人类因为寿命短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们会通过结婚的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,结成连理将生命维系下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对于寿命很畏的我们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,或许是没有意义的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很令人羡慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那句话 是咱从前…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,救…救命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,新世代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然还有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安 你待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这次我也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,金 要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要想只打败魔神的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就唯有攻击那个圣骑士体内的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一招了结它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等咱一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,咱现在就来救你 戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再生了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,休想妨碍金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,合技
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,十字射击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我被你抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那么兑现承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以答应金任何一个要求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 什么都可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,咱希望你回答咱一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你恢复当年的记忆了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这样回答你可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 所以你是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧 金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,戴安 关于今天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…咱…咱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,和你之间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,咱感觉发生了一件非常好的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,咱记得咱出门去找戴安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…然后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说你忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道啊 是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,咱好在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,咱这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52}时间啊 倒流吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,终
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的梅利奥达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我的伤太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还不是睡觉的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是你么 德雷弗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,亨德里克森
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我一看到你的脸就突然这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我犯了很多无法挽回的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:22:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定也做过对不起你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可以让我睡去了么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我的身体已经动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,德雷弗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,吾友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次站起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我等的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 七原罪 圣战的预兆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,爱的形状
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,剩饭长说了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,团长做菜那就是剩饭的预兆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真是遗憾的预兆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,遗憾的剩饭？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}霞光万道中你吹着口哨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:54.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}「明天见」「再会」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.76,OP,,0,0,0,,那理所当然的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:00.97,OP,,0,0,0,,竟被3、2、1、0重置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:04.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}神明大人也会一笑置之吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:10.69,OP,,0,0,0,,仰望天空 摆出一副幸福姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:15.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}摘下枯萎的最后一株幸运草
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:20.82,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}如果世界让你哭泣 我愿为你犯下任何罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:25.08,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}光明降临 Regret
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.71,OP,,0,0,0,,破坏吧 Never Ever Heaven's Blind World
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:31.33,OP,,0,0,0,,泡沫之梦消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:34.17,OP,,0,0,0,,曾几何时目及的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:38.63,OP,,0,0,0,,如果你能面露微笑 我愿为你承受任何惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:43.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}拂晓的Blurry Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:49.19,OP,,0,0,0,,明天若吹起口哨 小小的瞳孔深处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:54.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}必将闪现光辉未来
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:06.56,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}着眼于未来的背影中看不到一丝迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:14.94,ED,,0,0,0,,我的心中燃起了星星之火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:23.70,ED,,0,0,0,,我憧憬着你 跟着你的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:31.46,ED,,0,0,0,,回过神来已是气喘吁吁 我这才明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:40.59,ED,,0,0,0,,我未知的潜能 还被压在箱底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:49.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}黑暗之中黑天墨地 我用心中生锈的钥匙撬开箱子
